        Parameters:
        serialNumber - Device Serial Number
        isPosAndroid - The device is a Point Of Sale System
        manufacturerName - Device Manufacturer Name
        fullDeviceName - Full Device Name (deprecated, instead set 'modelName' and retrieve with 'manufacturerModel)
        osBuildNumber - OS build number. Requirements: Sequential number; Only numbers and dots; For each field between the points the amount of digits must be constant; Max of four fields between the points (e.g. 1.0.0.0). Examples of accepted Kernel Version: "AAMMDD", "AA.MM.DD"
        firmwareVersion - Device Firmware Version (deprecated, use osBuildNumber instead).
        modelName - Device Model Name.
        kernelVersion - Device Kernel Version. Requirements: Sequential number; Only numbers and dots; For each field between the points the amount of digits must be constant; Max of four fields between the points (e.g. 1.0.0.0). Examples of accepted Kernel Version: "AAMMDD", "AA.MM.DD"
        cpuInfo - Returns the hardware information of the CPU.
        iccReaderPosition - Position of ICC (Contact) Reader.
        magReaderPosition - Position of MAG STRIPE Reader.
        nfcReaderPosition - Position of NFC (Contactless) Reader.
        keyboardType - Type of keyboard referenced in enum KeyboardType.
        customResourceVersion - Custom Resource Version. Return CUSTOM_RESOURCE_UNKNOWN if not applicable.
